title: Anders Holm / Dupuytren's Contracture & Lasik Surgery
description: Sean’s affection for his dog gets him an ear infection and Priyanka prevents his panic over the arthritis in his foot. Anders Holm makes Sean squirm as he describes in detail his love for LASIK eye surgery and shares his experience inheriting Dupuytren's contracture.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
